---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Uptalent 2026 new website â€” initialization"
  description="Setup placeholder while core systems are configured"
>
  <section class="status">
    <h1>Initialization in progress</h1>
    <p>
      Astro scaffolding, MDX support, and content collections are configured. Page content and
      visual sections will be added only after the owner provides the approved `.md` files and the
      initialization checklist is complete.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Content source:</strong> awaiting `src/content/pages/*.mdx` from owner.</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Next steps:</strong> finalize shared components, configure external services, then
        request copy per page.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .status {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2vw + 1rem, 2.25rem);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
